'''孤䳍'''（[[學名|學名]]：''{{lang|la|Tinamus solitarius}}''）是[[巴西|巴西]]東部[[大西洋森林|大西洋森林]]特有的一種[[鳥類|鳥類]]。

==分類==
孤䳍屬於[[䳍科|䳍科]]。牠們一般能夠飛行，但不能長久。牠們是[[鴕鳥目|鴕鳥目]]的近親。<ref name="Davies">{{cite encyclopedia |last=Davies |first=S.J.J.F.|editor1-first=Michael |editor1-last= Hutchins|encyclopedia=Grzimek's Animal Life Encyclopedia |title=Tinamous |edition=2 |year=2003 |publisher=Gale Group|volume=8 Birds I Tinamous and Ratites to Hoatzins |location=Farmington Hills, MI|isbn=0 7876 5784 0 |pages=57-59}}</ref>以往牠們分為兩個[[亞種|亞種]]：[[巴西|巴西]]東北部的''Tinamus solitarius pernambucensis''及[[巴拉圭|巴拉圭]]東部南與[[阿根廷|阿根廷]]東北部的指名亞種''Tinamus solitarius solitarius''，不過前者並不獨特與指名亞種，只有個別的有特別的色彩。<ref name=Raposo2004>{{Cite journal en |author=Raposo do Amaral, Fábio Sarubbi  & Silveira, Luís Fábio |year=2004 |title=''Tinamus solitarius pernambucensis'' Berla, 1946 é sinônimo de ''Tinamus solitarius'' (Vieillot, 1819) |journal=Ararajuba |volume=12 |issue=1 |pages=33-41 |url=http://www.ib.usp.br/~lfsilveira/tinamus.pdf.pdf |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20070927203153/http://www.ib.usp.br/~lfsilveira/tinamus.pdf.pdf |archivedate=2007-09-27 |access-date=2009-03-31 }}</ref>

==特徵==
孤䳍平均長45厘米。<ref>{{cite book en |last1='''Harrison''' |first1=Colin |authorlink1= |last2=Greensmith |first2=Alan |editor1-first=Edward |editor1-last=Bunting  |title=Birds of the World |edition=First |year=1993 |publisher=Dorling Kindersley |location=New York, NY |isbn=1 56458 295 7 |page=42 |chapter=Non-asserines }}</ref>背部的色調由[[橄欖|橄欖]]色至銹色不等，頸下[[羽毛|羽毛]]的明暗部亦有不同，且有黑色斑紋。''Tinamus solitarius pernambucensis''的羽毛較黃，在[[頸部|頸部]]有較多斑紋。<ref name = cabot1992 />

==分佈==
孤䳍分佈在[[巴西|巴西]]的[[巴伊亞|巴伊亞]]東南部、[[米納斯吉拉斯|米納斯吉拉斯]]東部、[[聖埃斯皮里圖州|聖埃斯皮里圖州]]、[[里約熱內盧州|里約熱內盧州]]、[[聖保羅州|聖保羅州]]、[[南馬托格羅索州|南馬托格羅索州]]東部、[[巴拉那州|巴拉那州]]、[[聖卡塔琳娜州|聖卡塔琳娜州]]及[[南里奧格蘭德州|南里奧格蘭德州]]北部。牠們亦在[[巴拉圭|巴拉圭]]東南部及[[阿根廷|阿根廷]]東北部的[[米西奧內斯省_(阿根廷)|米西奧內斯省]]出沒。<ref name="BLI"/><ref>{{cite book |last1=Clements |first1=James |title=The Clements Checklist of the Birds of the World |edition=6 |year=2007 |publisher= Cornell University Press|location=Ithaca, NY |isbn=978 0 8014 4501 9}}</ref>

==行為==
[[Image:Tinamus_solitarius_nest.JPG|thumb]]
孤䳍會產形狀奇特的蛋，外表有光澤及充滿色彩。<ref name = cabot1992>{{Cite book en|author=Cabot, José|year=1992|chapter=Solitary Tinamou|editor=del Hoyo, Josep; Elliott, Andrew & Sargatal, Jordi (eds.)|title=Handbook of Birds of the World'' (Volume 1: Ostrich to Ducks)|pages=127, Plate 6|publisher=Lynx Edicions|location=Barcelona|id=ISBN 84-87334-10-5}}</ref>牠們主要吃[[果實|果實]]、[[種子|種子]]或低的[[植物|植物]]。雄鳥會在巢中孵化鳥蛋，且會照顧雛鳥一段短時間。<ref name="Davies"/>

==生態==
孤䳍棲息在低地潮濕的[[熱帶雨林|熱帶雨林]]及山區高達[[海拔|海拔]]1200米的[[森林|森林]]。<ref name="BLI"/>牠們棲息在[[次生林|次生林]]，且能容忍一定程度的間伐。牠們不喜歡種植外來[[植物|植物]]的地方。由於牠們的數量豐富，被獵殺仍未至瀕危的地步。有一些孤䳍生活在偏遠的森林[[交錯群落|交錯群落]]中，佔地只有約400公頃。<ref name="Simon (2000)">{{Cite journal en |author=Simon, José Eduardo |year=2000 |title=Composição da Avifauna da Estação Biológica de Santa Lúcia, Santa Teresa - ES |journal=Boletim do Museu de Biologia Mello Leitão N.S. |volume=11-12 |pages=149-170 |url=http://www.melloleitao.iphan.gov.br/boletim/arquivos/11_12/Artigo9_Boletim_11_12.pdf |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20070730145222/http://www.melloleitao.iphan.gov.br/boletim/arquivos/11_12/Artigo9_Boletim_11_12.pdf |archivedate=2007-07-30 |access-date=2009-03-31 }}</ref><ref name="Silveira (2005)">{{Cite journal en|author=Silveira, Luís Fábio; Develey, Pedro Ferreira; Pacheco, José Fernando & Whitney, Bret M.|year=2005|title=Avifauna of the Serra das Lontras–Javi montane complex, Bahia, Brazil|journal=Cotinga|volume=24|pages=45-54|url=http://www.ib.usp.br/~lfsilveira/lontras.pdf}}{{dead link|date=2017年12月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref>

==保育==
孤䳍現時因[[城市化|城市化]]、[[工業化|工業化]]、[[農業|農業]]發展及建設道路不斷的伐林而受到威脅。牠們因過度獵殺，[[世界自然保護聯盟|世界自然保護聯盟]]將牠們列為近危<ref name="BLI"/>，其分佈地只有990000平方公里。<ref name=BLI2008a>{{cite web | url=http://www.birdlife.org/datazone/species/index.html?action=SpcHTMDetails.asp&sid=12&m=0 | title=Solitary Tinamou - BirdLife Species Factsheet | accessdate=6 Feb 2009 | author=BirdLife International | year=2008(a) | work=Data Zone | archive-date=2009-01-05 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090105001238/http://www.birdlife.org/datazone/species/index.html?action=SpcHTMDetails.asp&sid=12&m=0 | dead-url=no }}</ref>以往分類為''T. s. pernambucensis''的群族已經非常罕有或已消失。北方的群族亦很稀有，歷史上就只有不多於6個標本。<ref name=BLI/><ref name=Raposo2004/><ref name=cabot1992/>

孤䳍較容易被引入到其他環境，在一些只有610公頃的森林地區，也可以見到牠們。<ref name=Faria2006>{{Cite journal en|author=Faria, Christiana M.A.; Rodrigues, Marcos; do Amaral, Frederico Q.; Módena, Érica & Fernandes, Alexandre M.|year=2006|title=Aves de um fragmento de Mata Atlântica no alto Rio Doce, Minas Gerais: colonização e extinção|journal=Revista Brasileira de Zoologia|volume=23|issue=4|pages=1217-1230|doi=10.1590/S0101-81752006000400032|url=http://www.scielo.br/pdf/rbzool/v23n4/32.pdf|access-date=2009-03-31|archive-date=2010-03-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100331083017/http://www.scielo.br/pdf/rbzool/v23n4/32.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref>

